title: Where Wall Street and Silicon Valley Intersect
title_page: Where Wall Street and Silicon Valley Intersect - The New York Times
maintext:
Wall Street and Silicon Valley Form an Uneasy Alliance
Entrepreneurs and venture capitalists have done their best to resist or reduce Wall Street’s entreaties, but it appears that a new relationship has begun to develop.
